description: Hololive is a virtual YouTuber (VTuber) agency owned by the Japanese tech entertainment company Cover Corporation. The brand gained popularity as a talent agency for popular VTubers, managing 75 talents with as of January 2023. Among them are the most subscribed active VTubers in Japan (Houshou Marine), Southeast Asia (Kobo Kanaeru), and North America (Gawr Gura).
